      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَمَّنْ نَسِيَ زِيَارَةَ اَلْبَيْتِ حَتَّى يَرْجِعَ إِلَى أَهْلِهِ فَقَالَ «لاَ يَضُرُّهُ إِذَا كَانَ قَدْ قَضَى مَنَاسِكَهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2784 - Hisham ibn Salim narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said: I asked him about someone who forgot to perform the visitation of the Kaaba (Tawaf al-Ziyara) and returned to their family.\nImam (as) said: \"It does not harm them if they have completed their other rites.\""
        ]
      }
